  - Title: Tejo-bindu Upanishad
    Location: I 18
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
  - 775
---
To direct the mental current towards the basic unity of all things and to
divert it from the observation of differences is ‘Observance’ (niyama);
therein lies transcendent bliss. It should be practised regularly by the
wise.
